How to play the game:

1. Start Game
1.1 When you run the program, a title screen will be shown. There are two buttons (as usual!). Click the "Play" button to start the rough Nin start version!

2. Control Logic
2.1 AD keys are used to move the little "knight." Meanwhile, W key is used to jump. (But jumping here has a buffer time and you must jump when you on the platform.)

2.2 On the left upper corner, you can see a "Back" button. Press it and then you can get back to the title screen (as usual).

3. Game Task
3.1 Have not decided yet.

4. Exit Game
4.1 Press "ESCAPE" key to exit game any time.

4.2 Or at the start of the game, click "Quit" button shown in the title screen to exit the game.